{"tid":1328101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk新搞作 研發人機連接介面 人腦植入晶片計畫有進展 盼明年人體試驗","createTime":"2019-07-17T22:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T03:36:04.000Z","uid":30561,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"128805e16cca5e41acbb528bed83ee40b2bf9a23","tid":1328101,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:08:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">馬斯克人腦植入晶片計畫有進展 盼明年人體試驗</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lA77zsJ31nA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlA77zsJ31nA&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=415fde41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lA77zsJ31nA</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社舊金山16日綜合外電報導）充滿未來主義構想的美國實業家馬斯克（Elon Musk）今晚揭露，他的神秘新創企業Neuralink在研發連結人腦和電腦的介面上已有所進展，並希望明年開始進行人體試驗。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，電動車大廠特斯拉（Tesla）的創辦人馬斯克長期以來竭力主張，人類可能被人工智慧（AI）超越，最佳情況下淪為「寵物貓」，為避免如此，人若能透過一個神經織網（neural lace）將頭腦和機器連結，將非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克和Neuralink的團隊成員今天在舊金山一場發表會中展示研發成果，並希望藉此招募在軟體、機器人、神經科學和其他領域的人才。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克在會中表示：「我們最終能製造出一個完全結合人腦和機器的介面，達成（人類）和AI的某種共生。」<br />\n<br />\nNeuralink在現場發表一個初步版本的微小感測器，附有髮絲般細線，可藉由專為執行高精密任務打造的機器人以微創方式植入人腦。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克說：「這些是微小電極，機器人會精巧植入它們」，且可有數千個電極和人腦連結。他還表示：「植入不會很麻煩，且將運作順暢，還有無線功能」。<br />\n<br />\n根據Neuralink說法，這顆晶片將以無線方式透過耳機對外溝通，將資訊傳遞給智慧手機裡的應用程式（app）。目前目標是讓植入晶片的人腦能用意念來操控手機，最終希望能拓展到操控其他裝置，例如機器人手臂。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克表示：「這具有龐大潛力。我們希望明年底前能讓一名病患安裝。」<br />\n<br />\nNeuralink團隊一名神經外科醫生透露，他們初步聚焦於協助解決腦部疾病和癱瘓，長遠目標則是讓植入技術足夠安全、可靠和輕易，提供想藉電腦運算能力強化腦力的人一些常規手術選項。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克又說，研發目標是讓強化人腦晶片植入技術，能和眼睛雷射手術一樣簡單。（譯者：張正芊/核稿：劉學源）1080717<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-tw/news/other/%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%85%A6%E6%A4%8D%E5%85%A5%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E6%9C%89%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95-%E7%9B%BC%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%94%E8%A9%A6%E9%A9%97/ar-AAEsBCV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnews%2Fother%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%2585%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%25A4%258D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%2599%25B6%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%2595%25AB%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25B1%2595-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597%2Far-AAEsBCV&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=b2186dd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-tw/news/other/%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%85%A6%E6%A4%8D%E5%85%A5%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E6%9C%89%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95-%E7%9B%BC%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%94%E8%A9%A6%E9%A9%97/ar-AAEsBCV</a>"},{"pid":"8222f18199d9860f0ec5f11b89fc244e07ff176b","tid":1328101,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:09:24.000Z","msg":"Why Elon Musk, Facebook and MIT Are Betting On Mind-Reading Technology?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R3G5fzz76lQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR3G5fzz76lQ&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=5dac1bf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R3G5fzz76lQ</a>"},{"pid":"29ca81e5f4679fe141f14e5fe39ed50033979d07","tid":1328101,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:10:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Elon Musk NeuraLink Full Presentation</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWxrOVtulpw&amp;t=836s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaWxrOVtulpw%26t%3D836s&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=d50237e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aWxrOVtulpw&amp;t=836s</a>"},{"pid":"bdd261edd50330b69e1eecef708c620257738455","tid":1328101,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:12:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SU9tOLFjsQU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSU9tOLFjsQU&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=7ae6e677\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SU9tOLFjsQU</a>"},{"pid":"52c84ce8e552a1b967cdbbc21bb81f398a6c1938","tid":1328101,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:18:02.000Z","msg":"好期待但唔知點解覺得恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d201261dcad9ba9a53df5aab2f9cf663fd6acf","tid":1328101,"uid":77084,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:18:37.000Z","msg":"植入狗狗個腦，明明係人會睇到係曱甴，拍死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09854818ec70594cd0bf401cfb1d06b35feacbcc","tid":1328101,"uid":20241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:20:47.000Z","msg":"　　&ldquo;要是這樣，還是有一部分人能支付得起的。&rdquo;<br />\n　　&ldquo;是的，但只是一小部分有產階層，社會海洋中那條連通上下層的管道徹底中斷了。完成超等教育的人的智力比普通人高出一個層次，他們與未接受超等教育的人之間的智力差異，就像後者與狗之間的差異一樣大。同樣的差異還表現在許多其他方面，比如藝術感受能力等。於是，這些超級知識階層就形成了自己的文化，而其余的人對這種文化完全不可理解，就像狗不理解交響樂一樣。超級知識分子可能都精通上百種語言，在某種場合，對某個人，都要按禮節使用相應的語言。在這種情況下，在超級知識階層看來，他們與普通民眾的交流，就像我們與狗的交流一樣簡陋了&hellip;&hellip;於是，一件事就自然而然地發生了，你是個聰明人，應該能想到。&rdquo;<br />\n　　&ldquo;富人和窮人已經不是同一個&hellip;&hellip;同一個&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;<br />\n　　&ldquo;富人和窮人已經不是同一個物種了，就像窮人和狗不是同一個物種一樣，窮人不再是人了。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e869aee91ef8b26595f6eb73e6eeb75516779be9","tid":1328101,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:21:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VzbSC6sM6DY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVzbSC6sM6DY&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=5ab787c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VzbSC6sM6DY</a>"},{"pid":"0162d108e4ca530e052