kgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3ffdea09cfc0cb6a7f935ab0dd9a8c4aa050cb","tid":1328101,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:29:35.000Z","msg":"然後支共間諜全面進場"},{"pid":"33193afb5fbcd01dc9300ab23f9d64528cacb066","tid":1328101,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09854818ec70594cd0bf401cfb1d06b35feacbcc","tid":1328101,"uid":20241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:20:47.000Z","msg":"　　&ldquo;要是這樣，還是有一部分人能支付得起的。&rdquo;<br />\n　　&ldquo;是的，但只是一小部分有產階層，社會海洋中那條連通上下層的管道徹底中斷了。完成超等教育的人的智力比普通人高出一個層次，他們與未接受超等教育的人之間的智力差異，就像後者與狗之間的差異一樣大。同樣的差異還表現在許多其他方面，比如藝術感受能力等。於是，這些超級知識階層就形成了自己的文化，而其余的人對這種文化完全不可理解，就像狗不理解交響樂一樣。超級知識分子可能都精通上百種語言，在某種場合，對某個人，都要按禮節使用相應的語言。在這種情況下，在超級知識階層看來，他們與普通民眾的交流，就像我們與狗的交流一樣簡陋了&hellip;&hellip;於是，一件事就自然而然地發生了，你是個聰明人，應該能想到。&rdquo;<br />\n　　&ldquo;富人和窮人已經不是同一個&hellip;&hellip;同一個&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;<br />\n　　&ldquo;富人和窮人已經不是同一個物種了，就像窮人和狗不是同一個物種一樣，窮人不再是人了。&rdquo;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71008a4de5c80bc0f0c1c30acbb6e21a43358a09","tid":1328101,"uid":61517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:40:48.000Z","msg":"分分鐘世界大戰..."},{"pid":"02984834c954dcd7ab092fa4de98380a12483585","tid":1328101,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Link start <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a860d08c71ea744f29d3d7b5f3bd31d6e793b69","tid":1328101,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:46:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>Neuralink是人工島討論重點，教育是人工島的重要行業，新技術更有利推動人性化教育改革。</strong><br />\n<br />\n本人一直認為教育是人工島嘅重要行業，人工島的法律可以用到重新建立，更有利於教育改革，隨着科技的發展，納米技術和晶片技術正在快速融合，這種融合將給我們的教育帶來一種劃時代的改變：教師可以植入人大腦的納米晶片，收集學生唔同嘅學習數據，甚至作出即時分析了解那一些學生出現學習障礙。這絕對不是天方夜譚，目前為止，這種技術已現雛形，與之相關的各種研究測試也在緊鑼密鼓的測試之中。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣的請入內討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=d614a73d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ</a>"},{"pid":"37e5c657e1f6f09857e043e66a3496d2675838cf","tid":1328101,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dba41361ebacff80dfd881da6a7e2c46c048ddbe","tid":1328101,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"52c84ce8e552a1b967cdbbc21bb81f398a6c1938","tid":1328101,"uid":15758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:18:02.000Z","msg":"好期待但唔知點解覺得恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:29:28.000Z","msg":"到時候你做任何決定，都唔知係AI幫你自主決定定係AI控制左你決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:48:19.000Z","msg":"AI奪取人類肉體既日子來了"},{"pid":"bb92ae5c328b6ba14071a6e2f025030156809b9a","tid":1328101,"uid":205013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:49:16.000Z","msg":"cyberpunk 2077<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c175e98829cf8aa6a9e59a8c352254a0e6b88f0","tid":1328101,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T22:53:52.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n而家科技發展得咁快 道德倫理個邊跟唔跟得到<br />\n唔好唔記得有D有十幾億畜生奴隸既賤種邪惡國家"},{"pid":"2382128df46ca9c454bc25104e564d6a81ae94ba","tid":1328101,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T23:11:54.000Z","msg":"本人主張，Neuralink這技術應該讓每一個人學習，因人工島的法律可以重新建立，所以人工島教育可重點包括這技術，因為一旦學生在人工島學了這種技術，便可以自行設計相關的電腦晶片給自己使用，加快自行學習，不需大量時間在學校學習繁冗複雜的知識。你是否也想在人工島的新法律下，自行設計自已的晶片植入自已大腦，來體驗一下科技的神奇體驗呢？<br />\n<br />\n有興趣的請入內討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=d614a73d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ</a>"},{"pid":"fc8df62e1afaa7367ba9cb6a8394532f8f31e63f","tid":1328101,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T23:20:13.000Z","msg":"咪又俾支那偷咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680a6b3fbf45ae595ad821c36d15b41d3ca7167b","tid":1328101,"uid":250905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T23:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kRP54F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kRP54F.jpg&h=9e0081d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3c6b634457b9b032a8cedb0a73b6bfc1a7558b2","tid":1328101,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T00:59:50.000Z","msg":"這舉動一但只係比一啲權貴階級或者獨裁者掌握，加個指令，便做到極權控制人類。所以學生應自行設計大腦晶片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1328257/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1328257/page/1</a>"}]}